settings.description: Mario finds himself in the Underground Bunker after taking on the air fleet, he must get through it without any mistakes. Or else...

Standard puzzle level. Nothing to buzz about. 

I see someone else found out about the acceleration move.
Luigi must take the hammer bro suit on his airship and take it to bowser.
i think i made this feel a lot like a standard level
Munchers and nipper plants are alive and happily active here.
Not a Rip-off of an existing series called "The 8 Worlds" I swear. This is the Desert Lake; it goes straight to the deserts underground bunker.

Travel through the full and scenic views of the plains!
There's many secrets hidden!
